#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.frexp.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.frexp"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.frexp.frexp:1 of
msgid "Decompose the elements of x into mantissa and twos exponent."
msgstr "将 x 的元素分解为尾数和二的幂次。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.frexp.frexp:3 of
msgid ""
"Returns (`mantissa`, `exponent`), where `x = mantissa * 2**exponent``. "
"The mantissa is lies in the open interval(-1, 1), while the twos exponent"
" is a signed integer."
msgstr ""
"返回 (`mantissa`, `exponent`)，其中 `x = mantissa * 2**exponent``。 尾数"
"位于开区间 (-1, 1) 内，而二的幂次是一个有符号整数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.frexp.frexp of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.frexp.frexp:7 of
msgid "Tensor of numbers to be decomposed."
msgstr "要分解的数字张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.frexp.frexp:9 of
msgid "Output tensor for the mantissa. Must have the same shape as `x`."
msgstr "用于存储尾数的输出张量。必须与 `x` 具有相同的形状。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.frexp.frexp:11 of
msgid "Output tensor for the exponent. Must have the same shape as `x`."
msgstr "用于存储指数的输出张量。必须与 `x` 具有相同的形状。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.frexp.frexp:13 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，则其形状必须可以广播到输入形状。如果未提供"
"或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（仅可作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.frexp.frexp:18 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.frexp.frexp of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.frexp.frexp:23 of
msgid ""
"**(mantissa, exponent)** -- `mantissa` is a float array with values "
"between -1 and 1. `exponent` is an int array which represents the "
"exponent of 2."
msgstr ""
"**(mantissa, exponent)** -- `mantissa` 是一个值在 -1 和 1 之间的浮点数组"
"。`exponent` 是一个表示 2 的幂次的整数数组。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.frexp.frexp of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.frexp.frexp:29 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ldexp`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.frexp.frexp:30 of
msgid "Compute ``y = x1 * 2**x2``, the inverse of `frexp`."
msgstr "计算 ``y = x1 * 2**x2``，即 `frexp` 的逆运算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.frexp.frexp:33 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.frexp.frexp:34 of
msgid "Complex dtypes are not supported, they will raise a TypeError."
msgstr "不支持复数数据类型，会引发 TypeError。"

